verbose_text: In vitro, Tec inhibited the expression levels of type X collagen, cyclooxigenase-2, matrix metalloproteinase (MMP) -3 and MMP-13, but enhanced the expression of Runx1, type II collagen and aggrecan in the presence of IL-1beta.
